Package fruitninja.model

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Apple
    The Apple class is an extension of the GameObject class.
    Bomb
    The Bomb class is an extension of the GameObject class.
    Field
    The field class is a model that contains the game object and the slashtrail in the game.
    GameObject
    The GameObject class is a model class which contains the position, size, worth and speed of a Game Object.
    Orange
    The Orange class is an extension of the GameObject class.
    Player
    The player class is a model holds the scores and lives of a player.
    SlashTrail
    The SlashTrail class holds the begin and end positions of a slash movement.
    Strawberry
    The Strawberry class is an extension of the GameObject class.
